Brother to Ale Alan Craig & Ale Dolly Parton

column17: VERY affectionate. His tail never stops wagging!

column15: This slightly shy boy needs that special home where he can feel secure and let his true personality blossom. He loves to play with other dogs.
Somewhat reserved at first, but once he warms up to you, he's one happy, loveable pup.
The definition of "extrovert," this energetic boy will keep you constantly entertained!
